                    <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-purple-100 p-4 rounded-lg border border-purple-200">
                        <h3 class="font-bold flex items-center text-purple-700">
                            <i data-lucide="arrow-up-right" class="mr-2" style="width: 20px; height: 20px;"></i>
                            DeFi (Decentralized Finance): The Ultimate Collab
                        </h3>
                        <div class="mt-3 bg-white p-3 rounded-lg border border-purple-200">
                            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Technical Definitions:</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
                                <li><span class="font-semibold">Lending Protocols:</span> Platforms where users can lend and borrow crypto assets.</li>
                                <li><span class="font-semibold">Yield Farming:</span> Strategy of providing liquidity to earn maximum returns.</li>
                                <li><span class="font-semibold">Liquidity Pools:</span> Smart contract-based pools of tokens used for trading.</li>
                                <li><span class="font-semibold">Automated Market Makers (AMM):</span> Smart contracts that create markets for any token pair.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-3 bg-purple-50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-purple-200">
                            <p class="font-semibold text-purple-700">Now explain it in pop terms:</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
                                <li><span class="font-semibold">Lending Protocols:</span> Like Spotify giving exposure to indie artists - you lend your platform (assets) and earn streaming revenue (interest)! 🎵</li>
                                <li><span class="font-semibold">Yield Farming:</span> Like artists doing multiple collabs and tours at once to maximize their exposure and earnings! 💫</li>
                                <li><span class="font-semibold">Liquidity Pools:</span> Like fan funding platforms where everyone contributes to support their favorite artists, creating a shared pool of resources! 🎟️</li>
                                <li><span class="font-semibold">AMM:</span> Like an AI DJ that automatically mixes tracks based on the crowd's energy - no human intermediary needed! 🎧</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-purple-100 p-4 rounded-lg border border-purple-200">
