                                <li><span class="font-semibold">Web3:</span> The decentralized internet built on blockchain technology.</li>
                                <li><span class="font-semibold">DAOs:</span> Decentralized Autonomous Organizations governed by token holders.</li>
                                <li><span class="font-semibold">Identity & Privacy:</span> Self-sovereign identity and privacy-preserving technologies.</li>
                                <li><span class="font-semibold">Interoperability:</span> The ability for different blockchains to communicate and share data.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-3 bg-purple-50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-purple-200">
